snippet.title: Rival Fury - A 3D Beat Em' Up Street Fighter - Steam Early Access Trailer. Arcade Style Rage Brawl!
snippet.description:
Show up your rivals with martial arts fury.

A new 3D/2.5D street brawler, launching on Steam Early Access on 2/2/22. Save 20% during launch week!

A retro genre with a modern spin. Familiar arcade controls but this time you fight in every direction. Punch kick and combo your way through 5 immersive levels.

Steam Link:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1686010/Rival_Fury/
